{
  "stem": "23350.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Well, anyway, in the evening, we were sitting there, we didn't know-- we were standing in there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "We didn't know what was going to happen to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then they opened up the door and let us out again, and we could mix with all the people in the barrack.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I couldn't believe it that this is happening to me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But when this happened the third time, another couple of weeks had went by, and every time, Josef Mengele, with his entourage, they arrived on one side of the barrack, walked in.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And they would say, this side, everybody stand up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "This side, everybody kneel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And they would be doing, maybe, this side at first.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And when he came out a third time-- by this time, I had met some cousins.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And I said to my cousin-- they asked me about my sister and I said, my sister has been sent away to work.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And when she-- they heard everything what happened to me, they said, you have to stay with us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We were holding on by our hands, not to go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "When they came to-- to do the selection, my cousins went through, but me, they pushed me this side.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I am no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "So when I could see this is happening three times already, I said, I can't be always having this luck.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "So at that moment-- my cousins were already out-- I quickly took my rag in my hand.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And, you know, the barrack was divided in the middle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "It had like a-- like a little wall like this from bricks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "So I went on top of that-- that-- when I could see whether I was watching, of course, I went across to the other side and kneeled down, because the others were not being selected.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
